    v1 = 0.82
    v2 = (((tmp + 0.64 * v0 + 0.77) / (v0 + 0.36 - v1 + 0.20)) - v0)
    v0 = 0.60
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.95)) + wp.cos(wp.exp(v1 + 0.86)))
